trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""></xref> base class representing a field or a property to be extracted from a workflow instance and its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""> </xref> basisklassen som representerer et felt eller en egenskap som skal trekkes ut fra en arbeidsflytforekomst og tilknyttede merknader.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] TrackingExtract is the `abstract` base class from which the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> class and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> class are derived.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]TrackingExtract er den `abstract` basisklasse som den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>klassen og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>klasse er hentet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> specifies a field or a property to be extracted from the activity associated with a tracking event and a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> specifies a field or a property to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>angir et felt eller en egenskap som skal trekkes ut aktiviteten tilknyttet en sporing-hendelse, og en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>angir et felt eller en egenskap som skal trekkes ut roten aktiviteten til arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, gets the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, henter merknader tilknyttet utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: Annotations are `strings` that you define that contain information to associate with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Kommentarer er `strings` du definerer som inneholder informasjon for å knytte til de utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> associated with the extracted data.
When implemented in a derived class, gets or sets the name of the field or property to be extracted.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir navnet på feltet eller egenskapen som skal trekkes ut.

trans-unit.source: Member can be set to specify a field or a property; a member of a field or a property; or a single element of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Medlemmet kan angis til å angi et felt eller en egenskap. et medlem av et felt eller en egenskap. eller ett enkelt element i et felt eller en egenskap (eller et medlem av enten) som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: For example, a single element in an `array` may be specified.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel ett enkelt element i en `array` kan angis.

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of a field or a property.
trans-unit.target: Punktet merket navnet på et felt eller en egenskap.
